{"tid":1472760,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"（反思）一國兩制，港人治港，高度自治","createTime":"2019-08-14T16:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T16:07:47.000Z","uid":265898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"df78f44470ba3bca22b07ca2ac688cc9a7995c63","tid":1472760,"uid":265898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:05:47.000Z","msg":"寫呢段文之前，反思左幾晚直到琴晚。<br />\n我地追求既原意就係一國兩制（<span style=\"color: red;\">真正雙普選</span>）<br />\n林奠呢條大仆街將我地扭曲成港獨，恐怖分子，真真正正令人心寒。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地堅决維護一國，你能給予真正的兩制？</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">直接雙普選將會是我地今次唯一既命題</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">談，可以！打，奉陪！欺，妄想！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好希望大家記得6位犠牲既義士，5百位被補義士！<br />\n我地勇武同和理非追求既野都係一樣，五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n維護一國，堅持兩制<br />\n實行雙普選<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港🇭🇰時代革命<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#割彈都吾割蓆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一位普通愛香港既人。2019-08-15"},{"pid":"b67ce1e0da45b4ca500d03f73dc1bebd649a33b2","tid":1472760,"uid":265898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-si